latestPosts.caption:
Gorgeous @sonamkapoor radiates elegance with @meera_mahadevia marble gold leaf engraving and filigree work bag, beautifully styled by @rheakapoor , who truly believes in celebrating Indian craftsmanship. 

Our deepest gratitude to master craftsman Dada for his stunning gold leaf work on marble♥️

Much gratitude to iconic stylist @rheakapoor for not just styling beauty, but for amplifying Indian tradition. 

Your appreciation of our handcrafted bags means more than words can express. By choosing to spotlight pieces born from intricate hand work - you are helping carry the legacy of remote Indian artisans into the world.

These hands, often unseen and unheard, now find their work celebrated because you chose to believe in what we create. You have helped us bridge tradition with relevance, heritage with high fashion.

Thank you for your trust, your vision, and for championing the soul of our craft♥️

Much gratitude to beautiful style icon @sonamkapoor -With your touch, their legacy travels further. Thank you for carrying not just style, but soul of Indian hand craftsmanship♥️

Big thank you to @abhilashatd for believing in our creativity. Your support uplifts every artisan behind our work♥️ 

Thank you, @forummmmm for your love for our creations ♥️
